CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778184360
OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FOn Thursday, they were all jailed for
OL,7,Flife with Matos handed a minimum term
OL,8,Fof 27 years and six months; Preddie
OL,9,Fgiven at least 27 years and Cowley 25
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FSentencing at the Old Bailey, Judge
OL,13,FMark Dennis KC told them: "This was a
OL,14,Fbrutal and cowardly attack, ambushing
OL,15,Fyour victim who was outnumbered and
OL,16,Fhad no opportunity to try and defend
OL,17,Fhimself against such violence."
OL,26,@uD@[OUyD@_O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
