OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778184360
OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FHe noted that Matos had engaged in
OL,7,Fthree acts of violence in 10 months
OL,8,Fand had been wearing an ankle tag at
OL,9,Fthe time of the killing after being
OL,10,Fgiven a suspended sentence for drug
OL,11,Fdealing.
OL,13,FThe court heard how the defendants
OL,14,Fwere caught after Matos's GPS tag
OL,15,Ftracked them cycling to the scene of
OL,16,Fthe attack in Hanworth Park, armed
OL,17,Fwith two knives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
