FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778184360
OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FMr Donnelly had also cycled there in
OL,7,Fhis role as a runner for a local drug-
OL,8,Fdealing business operated from a phone
OL,9,Fnumber called the "John line".
OL,11,FInstead of meeting customers, he was
OL,12,Ffatally stabbed in the neck and left
OL,13,Fto die in thick grass near his bicycle
OL,14,Fwhere he was found the next day.
OL,16,FHe was still carrying nearly 30
OL,17,Fpackages of heroin and crack cocaine
OL,18,Fand #300 in cash.
OL,26,@qD@SOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
