FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778184360
OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FThe "sustained and targeted" attack on
OL,7,FMr Donnelly took five minutes and was
OL,8,Fnot caught on camera or witnessed by
OL,9,Fanyone, jurors were told.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FAfterwards, the defendants rode out of
OL,17,Fthe park, with Matos changing his
OL,18,Fclothes at a friend's address and the
OL,19,Fother two defendants going to Cowley's
OL,20,Fhome.
OL,26,@nD@EOUnD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
