OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778184360
OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FAs well as being linked to the scene
OL,7,Fof the crime by GPS, Matos's DNA was
OL,8,Fidentified on an unlit cigarette
OL,9,Fbeside the body and he had the
OL,10,Fvictim's blood on the sleeve of his
OL,11,Fhoodie.
OL,13,FMatos, of Hounslow, Preddie, of
OL,14,FFeltham, and Cowley, of Hounslow, had
OL,15,Fdenied involvement in Mr Donnelly's
OL,16,Fdeath and were convicted of murder
OL,17,Fafter a retrial.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
