CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1778184360
OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement, Tyler
OL,7,FDonnelly's grandmother Shelley Packman
OL,8,Fdescribed him as a "football mad"
OL,9,FTottenham Hotspurs fan who was cheeky,
OL,10,Ffunny, kind hearted and loved animals,
OL,11,Fparticularly his dog Archie.
OL,13,FShe told the court: "Tyler was only 75
OL,14,Fdays into his 19th year when he was
OL,15,Ftaken from us in the most cruel and
OL,16,Fhorrific way.
OL,18,F"He should have walked through the
OL,19,Fdoor. Instead, he was left in a field
OL,20,Fin the dark on his own."
OL,26,@pD@TOUpD@aO]uD@UOUzD@AOU|D@XO]
