OL,3,CThree jailed for life for ambush
OL,4,Cmurder of 19-year-old
OL,6,FShe described the difficulty of
OL,7,Fsitting through two trials and hearing
OL,8,Fthe defendants laughing in court,
OL,9,Fsaying they showed "no remorse and no
OL,10,Fhumanity".
OL,26,@qD@TOUrD@IO]
